item.description:
Convert a folder of mp3 files to opus for audiobooks windows:
for %i in (*.mp3) do ffmpeg -i &#34;%i&#34; -c:a libopus -b:a 32k &#34;%~ni.ogg&#34; linux:
for f in *.mp3; do ffmpeg -i &#34;${f}&#34; -c:a libopus -b:a 32k &#34;${f%%.*}.ogg&#34;; done JPEG to JPEG XL windows:
for %i in (*.jpg) do cjxl &#34;%i&#34; &#34;%~ni.jxl&#34; linux:
for f in *.jpg; do cjxl &#34;${f}&#34; &#34;${f%%.*}.jxl&#34;; done Download youtube playlist using yt-dlp with index in filename yt-dlp -f &#34;bestvideo[height&lt;=1080]+bestaudio&#34; -o &#34;%(playlist_index)s-%(title)s.
